    public interface LexiconCreator
    An interface for factory classes for lexicons.

    Lexicon, WeightedLexiconCreator, LimitedWeightsLexiconCreator

    • Method Detail

      • create

        Lexicon create()
        Returns an empty lexicon.
        Returns:
        an empty lexicon.

      • create

        Lexicon create(Language language,
               Environment environment,
               int numOfAssociations)
        Returns a lexicon containing associations between numOfAssociations things from the given environment with random words from the given language.
        Parameters:
        language - a language to generate words for the created lexicon
        environment - an environment containing things to be included in the created lexicon
        numOfAssociations - number of associations to be initially added to the created lexicon
        Returns:
        a lexicon containing numOfAssociations associations of the things from the given environment with random words from the given language.
